{"type":"message","id":"a776c07e","parentId":"ab313899","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:44:32.624Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3rv9ojdyhcru_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thread contains 1 message(s)\n\n=== Message 1/1: 19dc59bf948f6e77 ===\nFrom: Royal Cove <no-reply@docuverus.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@gmail.com\nSubject: Your Rental Application with Royal Cove\nDate: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 17:07:06 +0000\n\n**THIS IS AN AUTOMATED EMAIL. DO NOT REPLY**\r\n\r\nDear Robert Galletta,\r\n\r\nThank you for your interest in applying with Royal Cove.\r\n\r\nIn order to process your application, your income, ID and related\r\ndocumentation needs to be verified. Please click here\r\n<https://prod-app.dvapply.com/admin/inviteLink/docupload_applicant/Property/206/RoyalCove/ed5cdef0-10ce-11f1-969c-2f5b014a0a00/655294?>\r\nto complete the verification process. If you have any problems accessing\r\nthis link, please copy and paste the following URL into your web browser\r\nweb address field:\r\n\r\nhttps://prod-app.dvapply.com/admin/inviteLink/docupload_applicant/Property/206/RoyalCove/ed5cdef0-10ce-11f1-969c-2f5b014a0a00/655294?\r\n\r\nRoyal Cove has partnered with Docuverus to facilitate this process. Please\r\nnote the following important reminders:\r\n\r\n - If prompted to upload a *copy of your* *ID, images must be clear,\r\ncomplete (no screen shots), and straight. *You can also use the QR code to\r\nuse your phone to capture images of your live ID.\r\n - If prompted to upload your *SSN card, *likewise*, images must be clear\r\nand complete.  *\r\n - For proof of income, *original PDF earnings statements *downloaded\r\ndirectly from your employer or payroll provider are required. \r\n - If you are self-employed or have non-employment income, you can also\r\nupload *original PDF bank statements* downloaded directly from your bank\r\nwebsite, but note that if you are uploading business statements, PERSONAL\r\nbank statements are also required..\r\n - Some managers or landlords may allow you the option to verify income or\r\nbanking by connecting directly with your bank. If you see the \"*Verify\r\nAnother Way*\" option, you can use this process either instead of or in\r\naddition to uploading PDF documents.\r\n\r\nPlease note that failure to complete the verification process or providing\r\nincorrect or unverifiable documents can either delay processing your\r\napplication or result in disqualification.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about eligibility requirements or about\r\nqualification determinations, please feel free to reach out to us at +1\r\n(845) 452-3450 or royalcove@lexingtonpg.com.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about the verification process or need help\r\ncompleting the verification process, Docuverus can be reached at\r\nsupport@docuverus.com <mailto:support@docuverus.com>.\r\n\r\nAgain, thank you for your interest in applying with us!\r\n\r\nLexington Property Group,\r\n\r\nRoyal Cove"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":517,"aggregated":"Thread contains 1 message(s)\n\n=== Message 1/1: 19dc59bf948f6e77 ===\nFrom: Royal Cove <no-reply@docuverus.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@gmail.com\nSubject: Your Rental Application with Royal Cove\nDate: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 17:07:06 +0000\n\n**THIS IS AN AUTOMATED EMAIL. DO NOT REPLY**\r\n\r\nDear Robert Galletta,\r\n\r\nThank you for your interest in applying with Royal Cove.\r\n\r\nIn order to process your application, your income, ID and related\r\ndocumentation needs to be verified. Please click here\r\n<https://prod-app.dvapply.com/admin/inviteLink/docupload_applicant/Property/206/RoyalCove/ed5cdef0-10ce-11f1-969c-2f5b014a0a00/655294?>\r\nto complete the verification process. If you have any problems accessing\r\nthis link, please copy and paste the following URL into your web browser\r\nweb address field:\r\n\r\nhttps://prod-app.dvapply.com/admin/inviteLink/docupload_applicant/Property/206/RoyalCove/ed5cdef0-10ce-11f1-969c-2f5b014a0a00/655294?\r\n\r\nRoyal Cove has partnered with Docuverus to facilitate this process. Please\r\nnote the following important reminders:\r\n\r\n - If prompted to upload a *copy of your* *ID, images must be clear,\r\ncomplete (no screen shots), and straight. *You can also use the QR code to\r\nuse your phone to capture images of your live ID.\r\n - If prompted to upload your *SSN card, *likewise*, images must be clear\r\nand complete.  *\r\n - For proof of income, *original PDF earnings statements *downloaded\r\ndirectly from your employer or payroll provider are required. \r\n - If you are self-employed or have non-employment income, you can also\r\nupload *original PDF bank statements* downloaded directly from your bank\r\nwebsite, but note that if you are uploading business statements, PERSONAL\r\nbank statements are also required..\r\n - Some managers or landlords may allow you the option to verify income or\r\nbanking by connecting directly with your bank. If you see the \"*Verify\r\nAnother Way*\" option, you can use this process either instead of or in\r\naddition to uploading PDF documents.\r\n\r\nPlease note that failure to complete the verification process or providing\r\nincorrect or unverifiable documents can either delay processing your\r\napplication or result in disqualification.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about eligibility requirements or about\r\nqualification determinations, please feel free to reach out to us at +1\r\n(845) 452-3450 or royalcove@lexingtonpg.com.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about the verification process or need help\r\ncompleting the verification process, Docuverus can be reached at\r\nsupport@docuverus.com <mailto:support@docuverus.com>.\r\n\r\nAgain, thank you for your interest in applying with us!\r\n\r\nLexington Property Group,\r\n\r\nRoyal Cove","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777139072624}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f04df14","parentId":"a776c07e","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:44:43.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full Royal Cove email. There's no Amy mentioned in this email. Bobby said he wants to reply to the email \"from Amy\" at Royal Cove. \n\nMaybe Amy is the property manager? I can see the email is from Royal Cove sent by Lexington Property Group, and they have a phone number and email for questions. But there's no specific Amy sender here.\n\nWait - maybe Bobby is referring to the person he should be communicating with at Royal Cove? Or maybe there was a separate email from Amy that I can't find?\n\nLet me ask Bobby for clarification - but wait, he said \"Amy\" - maybe there's an email I missed. Let me check all recent emails more carefully. Or maybe Bobby has a specific contact at Royal Cove named Amy.\n\n\nI should check if there are other emails from Royal Cove or any other communication that mentions Amy, but since I can't find anything, I should just ask Bobby to clarify which email he's referring to so I can help him draft the right response.\n","thinkingSignature":"ba72825a82f353d13a4ecfd1d457ccfe8d738f02c9d2ad7a3220e04cea0ba422"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nI found the Royal Cove email (the one sent today about your rental application), but I don't see any email **from Amy** in your inbox. The Royal Cove emails are from `no-reply@docuverus.com` and `royalcove@lexingtonpg.com` — no Amy there.\n\nDo you mean:\n1. **A different email from Amy** that I should search for differently?\n2. **Amy is the contact** you want to reach out to at Royal Cove (the property manager)?\n\nOr if you have the email Amy sent — forward it to me or paste it here and I'll draft the reply! 📧"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1041,"output":335,"cacheRead":29312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cach