{"type":"message","id":"6f895408","parentId":"659a96c0","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:47:12.301Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mcdx9mv3gblo_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nThank you for your interest in Royal Cove! Offering affordable Apartments located in the Town of Poughkeepsie.\nKindly Note: Availability is subject to change throughout the inquiry process.\n1 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $1825.00\n2 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2150.00\n3 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2595.00\n\nOnsite Amenities:\nExterior amenities include a swimming pool, playground areas, picnic & grill areas, dog parks and basketball court. Interior amenities include laundry room on site, fully renovated  units, business center, lounge area and fitness center.\nUtilities:\nHeat ,Hot water, garbage, sewer, landscaping, etc. are included.  Electric, cable and internet are additional and paid for by tenants.\nWhat you need to know before applying!\nPet Friendly! One-time pet fee: $400 per dog & $200 per cat. Monthly Pet Rent is $35 per Dog & $25 per cat. No aggressive breeds (Rottweilers, Pit-Bulls, German Shepherds, Dobermans, Chows, etc.).  At full maturity they cannot weigh more than 50lbs. 2 pet maximum.\nOur leases are for 1 year.\n$20 application fee per adult (non-refundable).  All adults residing in the unit must be screened.  The screening process will consist of a credit check, background check, and mandatory pet screening .  You must provide your full social security number for the screening process.\nTotal household NET income 2.5 times the monthly rent is required.    We look for a credit score of 600 or higher\nRhino Partner- Rhino Policies start as low as $9 per month*, compared to an upfront cash deposit.\nAs required per the lease agreement all new tenants will be enrolled in the Waiver Program at an additional $18 per month. Ask us how this program benefits you!\nSpectrum through the property rep starting at $49.99 a month\nPlease let us know if you have already applied to our sister properties: Royal Ledges Aor Royal Gardens\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJx1jUEOwiAURK_SsLalvyjQrrwKhQ82YiGUGhvj3YWNO3cvmTczb7InT6aG3HKOE6UpHMrr8EQV89bp8CCnhtyr4PG1rC6HtY0pREz5aF0Ke6RJe1Rbya4_Jbpapb1AaSSCGJjl1poLH80ZJGih55kPQEGIXgLvGe-AyXEU9Q3r29_RaphirLv3BZeC8PkCt98_GQ.MEUCIQCWTK6waHQ5m4oXXmmk0HWUWuJpREFHCvC4dLlg9W3LSQIgBWmuktwnm5U9QNOCLRJfbL_fBqb8ylv8lngBFhSNwTY>\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 13, 2026 11:12 AM\nTo: RC Leasing <rcleasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Looking for new apartment\n\n Hello, I hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6. We are relocating from Tenn\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-03755809cc10337ec572b1f12a6beedf]\nCaution: External (rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>)\nFirst-Time Sender   Details<removed-link>\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-97c0836b41e87f6018b00b7d2e96af51]\n  Report This Email<removed-link>\n\n Hello,\n\n\nI hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6.\n\n\nWe are relocating from Tennessee, and I do plan to come up in person to tour the apartment before moving.\n\n\nWe do have a dog named Finnly who is about 50 lbs, so we would also like to know about your pet policies, including any associated fees or restrictions.\n\n\nAdditionally, could you please provide details on what would be required upfront to secure a unit? Specifically, we’re interested in understanding the security deposit, any application or administrative fees, pet fees, and any other initial costs.\n\n\nCould you also let us know if you currently have any 1-bedroom units available, or if you expect any availability to open up before June 6?\n\n\nLastly, are you currently offering any move-in specials or promotions?\n\n\nThank you for your time, and we look forward to hearing from you.\n\n\nBest regards,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/image.png\"><#/part>\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2175,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nThank you for your interest in Royal Cove! Offering affordable Apartments located in the Town of Poughkeepsie.\nKindly Note: Availability is subject to change throughout the inquiry process.\n1 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $1825.00\n2 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2150.00\n3 Bedroom/ 1 Bath starting at $2595.00\n\nOnsite Amenities:\nExterior amenities include a swimming pool, playground areas, picnic & grill areas, dog parks and basketball court. Interior amenities include laundry room on site, fully renovated  units, business center, lounge area and fitness center.\nUtilities:\nHeat ,Hot water, garbage, sewer, landscaping, etc. are included.  Electric, cable and internet are additional and paid for by tenants.\nWhat you need to know before applying!\nPet Friendly! One-time pet fee: $400 per dog & $200 per cat. Monthly Pet Rent is $35 per Dog & $25 per cat. No aggressive breeds (Rottweilers, Pit-Bulls, German Shepherds, Dobermans, Chows, etc.).  At full maturity they cannot weigh more than 50lbs. 2 pet maximum.\nOur leases are for 1 year.\n$20 application fee per adult (non-refundable).  All adults residing in the unit must be screened.  The screening process will consist of a credit check, background check, and mandatory pet screening .  You must provide your full social security number for the screening process.\nTotal household NET income 2.5 times the monthly rent is required.    We look for a credit score of 600 or higher\nRhino Partner- Rhino Policies start as low as $9 per month*, compared to an upfront cash deposit.\nAs required per the lease agreement all new tenants will be enrolled in the Waiver Program at an additional $18 per month. Ask us how this program benefits you!\nSpectrum through the property rep starting at $49.99 a month\nPlease let us know if you have already applied to our sister properties: Royal Ledges Aor Royal Gardens\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJx1jUEOwiAURK_SsLalvyjQrrwKhQ82YiGUGhvj3YWNO3cvmTczb7InT6aG3HKOE6UpHMrr8EQV89bp8CCnhtyr4PG1rC6HtY0pREz5aF0Ke6RJe1Rbya4_Jbpapb1AaSSCGJjl1poLH80ZJGih55kPQEGIXgLvGe-AyXEU9Q3r29_RaphirLv3BZeC8PkCt98_GQ.MEUCIQCWTK6waHQ5m4oXXmmk0HWUWuJpREFHCvC4dLlg9W3LSQIgBWmuktwnm5U9QNOCLRJfbL_fBqb8ylv8lngBFhSNwTY>\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: Bobby Galletta <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 13, 2026 11:12 AM\nTo: RC Leasing <rcleasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Looking for new apartment\n\n Hello, I hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6. We are relocating from Tenn\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-03755809cc10337ec572b1f12a6beedf]\nCaution: External (rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>)\nFirst-Time Sender   Details<removed-link>\n[cid:inky-injection-inliner-97c0836b41e87f6018b00b7d2e96af51]\n  Report This Email<removed-link>\n\n Hello,\n\n\nI hope you’re doing well. My partner Logan and I are currently searching for a 1-bedroom apartment and are looking to move in by early June, ideally before June 6.\n\n\nWe are relocating from Tennessee, and I do plan to come up in person to tour the apartment before moving.\n\n\nWe do have a dog named Finnly who is about 50 lbs, so we would also like to know about your pet policies, including any associated fees or restrictions.\n\n\nAdditionally, could you please provide details on what would be required upfront to secure a unit? Specifically, we’re interested in understanding the security deposit, any application or administrative fees, pet fees, and any other initial costs.\n\n\nCould you also let us know if you currently have any 1-bedroom units available, or if you expect any availability to open up before June 6?\n\n\nLastly, are you currently offering any move-in specials or promotions?\n\n\nThank you for your time, and we look forward to hearing from you.\n\n\nBest regards,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/image.png\"><#/part>\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777139232301}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a5ee388","parentId":"6f895408","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:47:21.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have Amy Smith's email from RC Leasing. This is the email chain from April 13, 2026. The latest email is from Amy Smith at RC Leasing, responding to Bobby's inquiry about the apartment.\n\nNow Bobby wants to reply to Amy. The Royal Cove email he got today (April 25) was a follow-up from a different system (Docuverus) about completing the verification process.\n\nBut since Bobby wants to reply to Amy specifically, I should draft a reply to this email (ID 7) which is the latest from Amy Smith at RC Leasing.\n\nLet me draft a reply to Amy. I'll use himalaya to reply to message 7 on icloud account.\n","thinkingSignature":"ca825eb546f9905f3d5a9f8aeb9b69634d03c43dbab3691862808dcedc16f4d4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFound it! Amy Smith from RC Leasing (Royal Cove) replied to your inquiry on April 13. Here's the context:\n\nShe confirmed pricing: **1BR starting at $1,825/mo**, pet fee $400 (dogs), and the income requirement is 2.5x monthly rent with a 600+ credit score.\n\nWant me to draft a reply to Amy now? What would you like to say? Something like:\n- Confirm you're still interested and have submitted the application\n- Ask a follow-up question\n- Something else?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1344,"output":257,"cacheRead":36224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37825,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777139232308,"responseId":"063c312002bd2a38094a9c8cdc1d95aa"}}
