{"type":"message","id":"a39eb3c4","parentId":"bf559240","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:49:10.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to draft an email to Amy Smith at RC Leasing saying he submitted his part of the application and is waiting on Logan to do his part. Let me draft this email and send it via himalaya.\n","thinkingSignature":"4233a1145cef9d42687026992db3d26772790937e5152284f55006b1a0b0bc1b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9x6c1g5xjck8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' | himalaya -a icloud message write -H \"To: RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com\" -H \"Subject: Re: Looking for new apartment\" 2>&1 | grep -v \"WARN\\|Rectified\"\nHi Amy,\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":470,"output":221,"cacheRead":37504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777139341714,"responseId":"063c318e8e9a2aa2850a7f312147b903"}}
