{"type":"message","id":"9e48288b","parentId":"71027ed9","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:49:34.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compose the email. The message write command opens an editor. I need to write the email content to a temporary file and use the pipe approach differently.\n\nActually, let me try using the template approach or find another way to send without interactive editor. Let me check if I can use the SMTP directly to send via himalaya or another method.\n\nActually, let me try passing the body via stdin with the write command. But the write command opens $EDITOR. Let me try to create a draft using himalaya's template functionality.\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach would be to use Python and smtplib to send from the iCloud account directly, or use the Mac's Mail.app. \n\nLet me try setting EDITOR to a script that will supply the content, or use sendmail. Actually, let me just try using Python to send directly via smtp.mail.me.com with the credentials I have.\n","thinkingSignature":"da94a36515c20a295671beaa8b45dc7b3bba5b8cbe85e97852f8c7c24d56e9ad"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6ruln7wxedyq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'PYEOF' | python3\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\nfrom email.mime.multipart import MIMEMultipart\n\nmsg = MIMEMultipart()\nmsg['To'] = 'RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com'\nmsg['Subject'] = 'Re: Looking for new apartment'\nmsg['From'] = 'rtg.bobby@icloud.com'\n\nbody = \"\"\"Hi Amy,\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\"\"\"\n\nmsg.attach(MIMEText(body, 'plain'))\n\nwith smtplib.SMTP('smtp.mail.me.com', 587) as server:\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('rtg.bobby@icloud.com', 'hxvl-voty-tcfj-guqp')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    print(\"Email sent successfully!\")\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":384,"output":475,"cacheRead":38336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777139361014,"responseId":"063c31a1587eb6d0bdbbb0c37f2a2517"}}
