{"type":"message","id":"19be7af5","parentId":"c259d2f5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T17:49:41.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The email was sent successfully. Let me confirm to Bobby.\n","thinkingSignature":"63096b08b5d6c80587242aa049adf9032d51b57a9449667524dcddf29b0b864c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone! ✉️ Email sent to Amy at RC Leasing. Here's what went out:\n\n> **To:** RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com\n> **Subject:** Re: Looking for new apartment\n>\n> Hi Amy,\n>\n> I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n>\n> We are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n>\n> Thank you,\n> Robert Galletta\n\nLet me know if you want to add or change anything!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":367,"output":175,"cacheRead":38656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777139376497,"responseId":"063c31b06578daff301df0bbfbe9f458"}}
